<p>Using</p>  <pre><code>var user = await UserManager.FindByIdAsync(userId); </code></pre>  <p>inside </p>  <pre><code>TransactionScope scope = new TransactionScope(TransactionScopeAsyncFlowOption.Enabled) </code></pre>  <p>throws an EntityException:</p>  <p>"The underlying provider failed on Open." => "MSDTC on server 'MY-PC' is unavailable."</p>  <p>Why it happens?</p>  <p>P.S. App is running under Visual Studio IIS Express.</p>